  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下HealthTech系统的数据流。核心是从EMR同步模块开始，有两条路径：一条走Audit，一条走Bail，最终都要汇聚到DiagnosticEngine。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Audit和Bail都是HealthTech_EMR_Sync的实例对吧？那它们和Define的关系是？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Audit直接指向Define。但Bail不走Define，它要先经过LabAnalyzer，也就是Barg那个节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我把Bail到Barg的连线加上了。那Barg和Bail之间是双向的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，Barg还要回指Bail，形成一个校验闭环。另外Define也要连到Barg，这是诊断引擎向实验室发请求的通道。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Define到Barg已连接。我注意到还有个HIPAA_Vault节点Code，它的位置在哪？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Code是合规存储，所有诊断定义都要先经过它，所以Code指向Define。这是审计要求的关键路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "收到。但我看草稿里还有Risk、Signal、Place、Press这几个节点，它们和主流程的关系是？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这是异常监控链路。Risk触发Signal，Signal再通知Barg做应急处理。Place和Press是独立的物理层状态，Place指向Press表示位置到压感的映射。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Risk-Signal-Barg和Place-Press两条支线都画好了。整体布局是从左到右，EMR相关在左侧，Lab和Vault在右侧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Barg到Bail的箭头方向我刚才说反了。应该是Barg指向Bail，表示LabAnalyzer回写结果到EMR_Sync，不是双向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已修正，现在Barg→Bail是单向回写。整个流程验证通过：EMR双路径汇入诊断，经合规存储，实验室闭环，外加异常监控和物理传感两条独立支线。",
